WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:01.719 --> 00:01:02.240
Tongtong

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:04.599
I hereby solemnly declare

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:06.319
You're saved!

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:09.680
The other day online,

00:01:09.680 --> 00:01:10.840
I saw that competition

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:12.159
everyone's buzzing about.

00:01:12.719 --> 00:01:13.719
What's it called again?

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:15.000
Path to Immortality.

00:01:16.359 --> 00:01:17.280
Yeah, that's the name.

00:01:17.439 --> 00:01:19.480
Haven't had a real fight in ages.

00:01:20.159 --> 00:01:21.920
What if they're tricking you?

00:01:22.599 --> 00:01:24.400
Then Xiao Baojie's road to hell

00:01:24.400 --> 00:01:25.280
will be packed with company.

00:01:25.359 --> 00:01:26.519
You can't kill people.

00:01:27.079 --> 00:01:28.200
I'm just joking around.

00:01:28.480 --> 00:01:29.239
I'm a doctor.

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:31.760
A doctor who saves lives and heals all.

00:01:31.840 --> 00:01:32.799
How could I ever kill anyone?

00:01:34.319 --> 00:01:35.760
But guys like the thief,

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:37.040
Limpy, the Fool, that lot,

00:01:37.040 --> 00:01:38.599
with their darker tendencies,

00:01:38.760 --> 00:01:39.560
you never know with them.

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:40.560
As for you,

00:01:41.159 --> 00:01:43.400
that little guy already told you,

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:46.400
he can't authorize you to form a team.

00:01:46.719 --> 00:01:49.959
You'd better be ready to fight solo.

00:01:50.439 --> 00:01:51.560
If we can't win the championship,

00:01:51.760 --> 00:01:52.439
what then?

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:57.840
Then we execute Black Street's top-secret plan.

00:02:01.640 --> 00:02:02.519
Succeed,

00:02:02.799 --> 00:02:03.719
or die trying.

00:02:09.599 --> 00:02:11.159
The safest approach

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:15.879
is to each join a different city's team

00:02:16.439 --> 00:02:18.439
and lead them into the finals.

00:02:18.759 --> 00:02:19.439
That way,

00:02:19.879 --> 00:02:22.560
we'll have a lot more room to maneuver.

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:25.360
Divide and conquer, meet in the finals.

00:02:25.400 --> 00:02:26.280
That's a great idea.

00:02:27.080 --> 00:02:28.039
But,

00:02:28.199 --> 00:02:29.639
you guys aren't gonna screw it up, are you?

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:34.520
At our age,

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:36.680
nothing's a sure thing.

00:02:37.080 --> 00:02:39.080
I'm off to pack my bags.

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:42.159
Worry about yourself first.

00:02:42.439 --> 00:02:43.360
I'm going to find Limpy.

00:02:44.280 --> 00:02:45.240
I'll go find the Fool.

00:02:46.759 --> 00:02:47.960
Bunch of losers.

00:02:48.240 --> 00:02:49.840
Taking forever just to head out.

00:02:50.159 --> 00:02:50.960
See you in the finals.

00:02:52.159 --> 00:02:53.120
They're all gone.

00:02:53.439 --> 00:02:54.879
I'm gonna head home and grab some snacks.

00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:57.000
I'm off.

00:02:57.240 --> 00:02:58.159
Actually,

00:02:58.439 --> 00:03:00.639
there's no need to take risks for me.

00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:03.479
I'm doing fine right now.

00:03:06.879 --> 00:03:07.919
I'm simply

00:03:07.919 --> 00:03:09.800
interested in the arena fights, that's all.

00:03:16.719 --> 00:03:17.520
Don't worry.

00:03:17.719 --> 00:03:18.719
Don't overthink it.

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:20.240
Even if the world turns against you,

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:21.599
I'll still stand behind you.

00:03:21.599 --> 00:03:23.719
Why would the world turn against me?

00:03:26.199 --> 00:03:27.639
Because I'm standing behind you.

00:03:29.879 --> 00:03:30.560
As for the competition,

00:03:34.560 --> 00:03:35.960
if Madman drops the ball,

00:03:36.719 --> 00:03:37.520
worst case,

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:39.439
we'll bathe the Imperial Capital in blood.

00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:48.000
In the middle of the day,

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.560
why call an elders' meeting?

00:03:50.280 --> 00:03:52.039
You made me lose my game.

00:03:56.199 --> 00:03:59.639
What did you call this meeting for?

00:04:01.039 --> 00:04:04.840
This Blessed Ones gathering in the Imperial Capital

00:04:05.199 --> 00:04:06.879
is called the Path to Immortality contest.

00:04:07.159 --> 00:04:07.919
Right, right, right.

00:04:08.080 --> 00:04:09.520
The Path to Immortality contest.

00:04:09.759 --> 00:04:13.599
It represents the face of Shanhai City.

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:15.639
So when it comes to selection,

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:18.439
we must consider the candidates carefully.

00:04:18.680 --> 00:04:20.079
This is too complicated.

00:04:20.319 --> 00:04:22.560
Let's just leave it to Xiao Feng.

00:04:27.279 --> 00:04:29.480
With the Immortal Realm now in limbo,

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:32.040
the future is uncertain.

00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:34.839
This Path to Immortality contest

00:04:34.920 --> 00:04:37.720
naturally becomes our top priority.

00:04:38.120 --> 00:04:39.639
So regarding the slots,

00:04:39.639 --> 00:04:42.680
I hear your grandson was blessed.

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:44.600
That boy

00:04:44.759 --> 00:04:46.399
is hardly worth mentioning.

00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:48.560
Then give him a slot,

00:04:48.639 --> 00:04:50.040
let him gain some experience.

00:04:50.360 --> 00:04:52.279
If he comes back with a prize,

00:04:52.879 --> 00:04:55.600
it'll be easier for him to run the group.

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:57.079
Well, well...

00:04:58.759 --> 00:05:01.319
Your grandson is a born prodigy.

00:05:01.439 --> 00:05:02.560
He'll have no problem.

00:05:03.839 --> 00:05:05.160
Since you've said

00:05:05.199 --> 00:05:07.120
the contest is so important

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:08.959
to Shanhai City,

00:05:09.759 --> 00:05:12.040
then the rest of the selections

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:14.160
become extremely important.

00:05:14.639 --> 00:05:17.120
We can't let any riffraff

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:18.160
just squeeze their way in,

00:05:18.399 --> 00:05:20.879
and make your grandson lose face for nothing.

00:05:21.360 --> 00:05:22.240
Don't you agree?

00:05:22.480 --> 00:05:24.199
That's exactly what I think.

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:27.639
Xiao Feng,

00:05:28.319 --> 00:05:30.519
arrange the other slots as you see fit.

00:05:31.240 --> 00:05:33.360
Strength must come first.

00:05:34.120 --> 00:05:35.920
If any elders have candidates,

00:05:35.920 --> 00:05:36.920
feel free to propose them.

00:05:37.079 --> 00:05:39.079
The strong rise,

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:40.399
the weak step aside.

00:05:43.959 --> 00:05:45.879
Elders, what do you think?

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:47.040
Anything else?

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:51.480
Then let's adjourn.

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:53.360
Well, we'll take our leave.

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:54.160
Fine. I won't see you out.

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:54.959
We're leaving.

00:05:55.199 --> 00:05:55.959
Goodbye.

00:06:02.399 --> 00:06:04.720
A bunch of geezers with one foot in the grave.

00:06:04.720 --> 00:06:05.680
See a juicy piece of meat,

00:06:06.480 --> 00:06:08.079
and they run faster than young people.

00:06:08.240 --> 00:06:08.920
Indeed.

00:06:09.560 --> 00:06:11.439
Right now, public curiosity

00:06:11.439 --> 00:06:12.560
about the Blessed Ones is at its peak.

00:06:12.879 --> 00:06:15.399
The contest is drawing the most attention.

00:06:15.839 --> 00:06:17.439
Competing at this time

00:06:17.439 --> 00:06:19.000
brings endless benefits.

00:06:19.560 --> 00:06:20.399
Who wouldn't want

00:06:20.399 --> 00:06:22.439
to plant their own man inside?

00:06:22.560 --> 00:06:23.160
Right?

00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:25.079
A bunch of old ghosts who've lived too long.

00:06:25.240 --> 00:06:26.279
Next time they beg you,

00:06:26.399 --> 00:06:27.360
you should just curse them out.

00:06:27.360 --> 00:06:29.279
Handle the rest yourself.

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:42.319
Master,

00:06:42.639 --> 00:06:44.560
cracking the slab without shattering it,

00:06:44.720 --> 00:06:45.879
I can already do it.

00:06:47.439 --> 00:06:48.759
You've only practiced a few days.

00:06:48.759 --> 00:06:49.879
Reaching this level

00:06:49.879 --> 00:06:50.800
is already quite good.

00:06:50.800 --> 00:06:52.360
How many days

00:06:52.519 --> 00:06:55.319
have you been here now?

00:06:57.839 --> 00:06:59.040
I've already wired the tuition over.

00:06:59.160 --> 00:07:00.879
Last lesson I taught you this,

00:07:00.879 --> 00:07:02.360
hardness against hardness.

00:07:02.560 --> 00:07:05.040
Today I'll teach you hardness against softness.

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:06.360
Your eldest senior brother,

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:07.519
Madman,

00:07:07.600 --> 00:07:09.040
took only half a day.

00:07:09.519 --> 00:07:11.519
Limpy took one full day.

00:07:11.720 --> 00:07:13.439
How long will you take?

00:07:13.639 --> 00:07:14.839
Practice hard.

00:07:15.000 --> 00:07:15.759
I'll definitely practice hard.

00:07:15.759 --> 00:07:16.399
Good.

00:07:16.399 --> 00:07:17.680
Next week's tuition,

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:19.480
I'll wire it to you right away.

00:07:22.439 --> 00:07:25.399
A martial artist must master both hard and soft.

00:07:25.920 --> 00:07:28.279
When you can, with body strength alone,

00:07:28.279 --> 00:07:29.240
with one palm strike

00:07:29.480 --> 00:07:31.199
hit the water inside the vat

00:07:31.199 --> 00:07:32.879
and make the vat burst,

00:07:33.279 --> 00:07:34.480
then you'll have graduated.

00:07:45.519 --> 00:07:48.040
That idiot Xu Siguo.

00:07:48.279 --> 00:07:50.120
Why can't we reach him?

00:07:50.319 --> 00:07:52.199
Why has he gone missing?

00:07:52.720 --> 00:07:53.519
You tell me.

00:07:53.839 --> 00:07:55.839
Could he have been kidnapped?

00:07:55.920 --> 00:07:56.680
Or maybe...

00:07:56.879 --> 00:07:57.959
he's already dead.

00:07:58.920 --> 00:07:59.680
Forget it, enough about that.

00:08:01.040 --> 00:08:01.600
Here's what we'll do.

00:08:01.879 --> 00:08:03.680
Go to the Black Street.

00:08:03.879 --> 00:08:04.800
Notify Su Yang.

00:08:05.040 --> 00:08:05.759
Tell him

00:08:06.240 --> 00:08:07.720
that at eight tomorrow morning,

00:08:07.879 --> 00:08:09.240
he needs to be at the Lingxiao training ground

00:08:09.519 --> 00:08:11.079
to take the selection test.

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:11.879
The test will last

00:08:12.279 --> 00:08:12.959
two days.

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:15.199
As long as he's compassionate,

00:08:15.800 --> 00:08:16.560
kind,

00:08:17.639 --> 00:08:18.319
and brave,

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:22.120
he can pass the test easily.

00:08:22.920 --> 00:08:23.600
Understood?

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:33.000
The Path to Immortality contest with a hundred cities

00:08:33.080 --> 00:08:35.240
should pull in plenty of sponsorships.

00:08:36.039 --> 00:08:36.960
Another fortune to be made.

00:08:38.360 --> 00:08:39.679
We're getting rich!

00:08:46.600 --> 00:08:47.840
He can't really be dead, can he?

00:08:48.960 --> 00:08:50.440
Then we'd have to find another one.

00:08:59.519 --> 00:09:00.559
About Limpy,

00:09:00.759 --> 00:09:02.519
don't let that stone face fool you.

00:09:03.159 --> 00:09:04.159
Deep down,

00:09:04.279 --> 00:09:05.080
he's actually really twisted.

00:09:05.879 --> 00:09:06.879
While you're staying there these two days,

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:08.200
you must be careful and cautious.

00:09:08.279 --> 00:09:08.799
Got it?

00:09:08.960 --> 00:09:10.960
Uncle Limpy is a really nice person.

00:09:11.080 --> 00:09:12.320
That's just on the surface.

00:09:12.320 --> 00:09:14.080
Inside, he's a total creep.

00:09:14.600 --> 00:09:16.279
Then I'll go play with Brother Fool.

00:09:21.840 --> 00:09:23.159
Actually,

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:25.519
Limpy is a pretty good guy.

00:09:25.679 --> 00:09:26.440
Responsible,

00:09:26.919 --> 00:09:27.600
sensible,

00:09:28.039 --> 00:09:29.120
tough on the outside, soft on the inside.

00:09:29.679 --> 00:09:30.960
Who knows, maybe one day,

00:09:31.080 --> 00:09:32.039
if his other leg gets crippled,

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:33.879
he'll evolve into the ultimate saint.

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:35.000
I'm full.

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:35.879
Go on, then.

00:09:36.159 --> 00:09:38.000
He's probably standing on that lame leg of his,

00:09:38.080 --> 00:09:38.960
waiting for you at the door.

00:09:46.759 --> 00:09:48.279
Limpy may be wicked,

00:09:48.360 --> 00:09:49.360
but he's bad with words.

00:09:50.600 --> 00:09:53.000
If that manipulative Fool sweet-talks her a few days,

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:55.639
that'd be a real problem.

00:10:00.960 --> 00:10:01.759
Wait a minute.

00:10:02.639 --> 00:10:03.879
What am I happy about?

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:06.639
At the end of the day,

00:10:06.799 --> 00:10:08.159
isn't Limpy the one benefiting here?

00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:09.679
I'm actually happy

00:10:09.679 --> 00:10:11.399
that she's with Limpy instead of the Fool?

00:10:11.399 --> 00:10:12.600
Why am I glad about that?

00:10:14.519 --> 00:10:15.159
Am I...

00:10:16.000 --> 00:10:17.639
Am I really that afraid of the Fool?

00:10:26.480 --> 00:10:27.639
Candidate Number One is in position.

00:10:27.879 --> 00:10:28.919
The assessment is about to begin.

00:10:33.080 --> 00:10:34.000
I hope he remembers

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:36.200
those keywords I hinted at yesterday.

00:10:36.720 --> 00:10:38.159
After all, the Imperial Capital

00:10:38.639 --> 00:10:40.919
really does care about contestants'

00:10:41.039 --> 00:10:42.240
basic moral character.

00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:46.759
Here we go, here we go.

00:10:46.759 --> 00:10:47.200
Come on.

00:10:47.279 --> 00:10:47.879
Hurry.

00:10:50.080 --> 00:10:51.320
Help!

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:53.919
Somebody help me!

00:10:55.039 --> 00:10:56.320
Where do you think you're running?

00:10:56.519 --> 00:10:58.120
Even if you scream your throat raw today,

00:10:58.120 --> 00:10:59.879
no one's going to come save you.

00:11:00.679 --> 00:11:02.080
Just give in to me.

00:11:02.679 --> 00:11:04.240
Help me!

00:11:05.799 --> 00:11:09.159
Faced with a top beauty I picked myself,

00:11:09.240 --> 00:11:11.519
plus a criminal who looks disgusting

00:11:11.519 --> 00:11:13.600
with absolutely no combat ability,

00:11:13.840 --> 00:11:14.759
I refuse to believe

00:11:14.759 --> 00:11:17.200
any man would stay unmoved in this situation.

00:11:18.120 --> 00:11:19.120
A hero saving a damsel in distress

00:11:19.279 --> 00:11:21.480
is every man's lifelong fantasy.

00:11:21.559 --> 00:11:22.840
Help!

00:11:23.639 --> 00:11:25.440
Save me, please save me!

00:11:25.799 --> 00:11:27.080
He doesn't even have a weapon!

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:30.559
Don't walk away!

00:11:30.720 --> 00:11:32.200
How about you give saving me a try?

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:35.399
Come on, just try saving me, will you?

00:11:38.120 --> 00:11:39.159
Please save me!

00:11:40.240 --> 00:11:40.879
Reporting in.

00:11:41.399 --> 00:11:42.559
Su Yang didn't save her.

00:11:42.879 --> 00:11:44.320
He even seemed to say "go for it."

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:45.480
Save me!

00:11:47.200 --> 00:11:48.320
Hey, don't walk away!

00:11:48.440 --> 00:11:50.240
Just try saving me, would you?

00:11:51.879 --> 00:11:53.200
My heart hurts.

00:11:53.399 --> 00:11:54.879
I can't move.

00:11:57.559 --> 00:11:59.200
Is something off with his orientation?

00:11:59.320 --> 00:12:00.200
I mean, am I...

00:12:00.200 --> 00:12:01.879
am I not attractive enough?

00:12:02.279 --> 00:12:03.840
You're attractive.

00:12:04.159 --> 00:12:05.360
Fine, fine, whatever.

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:06.320
Young Master,

00:12:06.679 --> 00:12:08.879
I've never seen anyone so devoid of morals.

00:12:09.240 --> 00:12:09.919
Just now,

00:12:10.080 --> 00:12:11.600
even I wanted to step in and save her.

00:12:12.039 --> 00:12:13.399
We have to mark him down for moral depravity.

00:12:13.399 --> 00:12:15.559
You absolutely cannot mark it like that.

00:12:16.440 --> 00:12:17.120
What do you know?

00:12:17.559 --> 00:12:18.440
What he just did...

00:12:19.399 --> 00:12:20.440
What he did...

00:12:21.879 --> 00:12:23.919
He wisely saw through

00:12:23.919 --> 00:12:25.159
the nature of this assessment.

00:12:25.519 --> 00:12:27.360
Sharp powers of perception,

00:12:27.600 --> 00:12:28.960
exceptional intelligence,

00:12:28.960 --> 00:12:31.000
and unshakable composure.

00:12:32.919 --> 00:12:33.879
Just

00:12:34.799 --> 00:12:35.759
write it down the way I said.

00:12:44.519 --> 00:12:45.559
Let's hope the next round

00:12:45.720 --> 00:12:47.000
goes off smoothly.

00:12:47.240 --> 00:12:48.480
The next one will absolutely be fine.

00:12:48.799 --> 00:12:50.200
To guarantee Su Yang passes

00:12:50.200 --> 00:12:51.240
the luck test smoothly,

00:12:51.360 --> 00:12:53.120
I specifically set up a deadly shooting game.

00:12:53.519 --> 00:12:54.759
Inside this revolver,

00:12:55.039 --> 00:12:56.159
there's only one paint bullet.

00:12:56.399 --> 00:12:57.519
I had someone load the paint bullet

00:12:57.639 --> 00:12:58.759
into the third chamber.

00:12:59.000 --> 00:13:00.840
And his opponent shoots first.

00:13:01.480 --> 00:13:02.360
No matter what,

00:13:02.759 --> 00:13:03.720
Su Yang wins.

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:06.879
Nicely done.

00:13:08.240 --> 00:13:09.279
The one on the right goes first.

00:13:23.279 --> 00:13:24.120
I have to say,

00:13:24.639 --> 00:13:25.799
you're really unlucky.

00:13:26.399 --> 00:13:27.279
My luck

00:13:27.639 --> 00:13:28.679
has always been incredibly good.

00:13:29.399 --> 00:13:31.000
For luck-based games like this,

00:13:31.639 --> 00:13:32.519
to me,

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:34.879
it's no different from an open-book exam.

00:13:47.919 --> 00:13:50.159
I feel like my luck's always been pretty good too.

00:13:50.600 --> 00:13:52.159
I was planning to fire four shots in a row.

00:13:52.960 --> 00:13:54.080
One shot each.

00:13:54.720 --> 00:13:55.519
You never said that.

00:14:08.240 --> 00:14:09.200
Hold on.

00:14:10.159 --> 00:14:11.679
Is he out of his mind?

00:14:12.039 --> 00:14:13.600
It was supposed to be one shot each.

00:14:13.600 --> 00:14:14.799
Is he playing games here?

00:14:14.879 --> 00:14:15.519
And you.

00:14:15.759 --> 00:14:16.399
You.

00:14:16.879 --> 00:14:18.759
You could've put the bullet in the first chamber,

00:14:18.759 --> 00:14:20.279
and let Su Yang win right away!

00:14:21.039 --> 00:14:21.679
I...

00:14:21.960 --> 00:14:23.600
How am I supposed to write this?

00:14:26.759 --> 00:14:27.720
Just write...

00:14:28.759 --> 00:14:29.639
Su Yang

00:14:30.080 --> 00:14:32.159
would rather sacrifice himself

00:14:32.320 --> 00:14:34.600
than let his opponent face danger.

00:14:34.720 --> 00:14:35.519
Highly responsible.

00:14:35.679 --> 00:14:36.559
Full of conviction.

00:14:36.840 --> 00:14:38.039
He perfectly fulfilled

00:14:38.039 --> 00:14:40.559
all the duties and obligations of a captain.

00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:41.840
Got it.